<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edle frawe, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan> Toplers,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        willen daran geweiset, daz er <add>die</add> ladung, als er auf das
                        lantgericht getan het, ablassen wil. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, wenn es der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> sein scheimbot</add>
<expan>vord<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz im <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> slewnigs
                                <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> werde. Und wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gediene<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>leta<ex>r</ex>e</expan>.</ab>
</div>
